
1.  Design Problem - Student management system

2.  List all the information that is needed to track the problems
            - Address
                    Email : (string)
                    Phone Number : (int)
                    Center : (string)

            - Person
                    First Name : (string)
                    Last Name : (string)
                    Dob : (date)

            - student
                    Id No : (string)

            - course
                    Course Name : (string)
                    Course code : (string)
                    Credit hours : (int)
                    ECTS : (int)
                    contact hours : (float)
                    Tutorial hours : (float)

            - instructor 
                    Course Teaching : (string)

            - Grade
                    Term
                        per course Mark: (float)
                        per course Char Grade: (char)

                    Year
                        per term : (float)
                        per term Char Grade: (char)
                    CGPA
                        per year : (float)
                        per year Char Grade: (char)

            - Enrol 
                    -Status : (string)

3. Design the front-end with Figma
